.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係有咁大分別架啦，男人同女人都入唔同廁所啦，有乜好嘈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩，就係呢種價值觀，連登啲言論一直停留起腦部未開登嘅質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢條撚樣讀過書未 定係藍絲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就算連登安答要侮辱個男受害者都唔會用你呢d唔好笑唔夠賤格既說話黎恥笑個男受害者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2ac3037750f7a249bc0eb44058472a65fb73ca","tid":241304,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"樓主真人肯定係垃撚圾女人仔一件 比男人恰既賤種美極狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89456fe9344d0d19a98ee3c248f6fc2f1ac055c7","tid":241304,"uid":47160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"如果係咪係囉，可惜唔係"},{"pid":"f795568e7d5e0b0a427dc97070ba42f7fde98efe","tid":241304,"uid":108972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T19:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主真人肯定係垃撚圾女人仔一件 比男人恰既賤種美極狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦，冇point就攻擊性別,可惜我令你失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地真係冇得救"},{"pid":"e07597849851242c7b778ae371231b2670033b48","tid":241304,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T20:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主真人肯定係垃撚圾女人仔一件 比男人恰既賤種美極狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦，冇point就攻擊性別,可惜我令你失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地真係冇得救</blockquote><br />\n你有冇point就大家